<br />
Hey i just had to ask about this one. Ive been looking all over every eq related site i know for the answers to this but it doesnt look like anyone really knows. Ive been tryin to camp the Iksar hide mask for like 2 days now, id go kill foragers/hunters trying to get Dronik to spawn. Only problem is every time i do it some person comes in and screws up the cycle so that no foragers/hunters/harbringer dronik will spawn. I was wondering if theres any way i can restart this cycle or if not how long it takes before the foragers/hunters start spawning again. Also if anyone whos reading this has done this camp before id like to hear of your experiance with it, ie time it took to get him to spawn and how the actual fight went. I play on tribunal and am saving up for a troubadors mace (10k) and i really dont wanna have to pay the 10k that the mask also sells for. Thanks ahad of time for the input!
<br />
Littul Jonn
<br />
50 bard on Tribunal
