				<td colspan="2"><span>First off - only kill the foragers - the hunters are on a different cycle and have crap for loot.
<br />
After every forager kill - either another forager spawns or a random named spawns that is the Ph - you need to find that mob and kill it(sometimes good loot - ikky bp, and mask are nicest). Sometimes it takes a while to find the named - if thats the case he may be wandering down around that graveyard.
<br />

<br />
Menolian
