				<td colspan="2"><span>Long time since I did this so not sure if anything have changed.
<br />

<br />
We used to have a group sitting at the cave and I would follow the stream while using track..between the cave and the lake I would 90% of the time pick up both the forager and the hunter (or the named) on track. On rare occasions I would first pick up the track on the other side of the lake (aqueduct side).
<br />

<br />
As menolian mentions the cycle just continues and if nothing on track then it's because the mob is out of range... or god forbid SOE really did break the cycle  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-3.gif" border="0" alt="Scared" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
