				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Iksar Hide Mask...<a name="57776"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 20 04 8:40 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I followed advice to hang out around the area from the Swamp of No Hope ZI, along the little stream, to the large pool it runs into. I'd track Foragers from this area, they all seemed to spawn close by and I'd kill them as soon as they popped at the top of my track list.
<br />

<br />
Did this for a couple of nights, and got no results, just the no drop stuff from various named and also a Hangman's Noose. I couldn't work out why that floating little git Dronik wasn't popping. Sometimes the cycle just seemed to stop, or kind of jam up with non-stop Hunters.
<br />

<br />
Eventually I changed my tactic to sweeping round with track in a larger area, still using the stream as a centre point. I found that once in a while Foragers were spawning at a point quite a way behind me, which I hadn't really been checking. When I started killing them, the cycle flowed smoothly and I got the mask after a few hours.</span></td>
