				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey Guys!
<br />
I got the mask on the first attempt thanks to you guys! Heres how it went down. I came into TT and started killing foragers by the river, then after a about an hour or so i got Droknik to spawn. Ran up had elemental rythems playing and started to chant him down. He casted alot but i resisted most of it, only landed root a couple of times. So i kill him and get the mask then my buddy goes, check track. So i check track and a second dronik spawned! So he brings his druid (pretty much unequpied ) down to get that mask, except i didnt kill dronik, had like 5 adds and he landed a pretty mean snare on me so i got killed. But after comein back down i whooped him once more and got his mask. So all in all i think it was a great camp and i sold one of the masks to buy a troubadors mace. Thanks for all the info, hope this helps anyone else whos trying to get this!
<br />
Littul Jonn
<br />
52 Minstrel of the Tribunal</span></td>
